file.name: multi-media-types.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0"
info:
  title: Simple
paths:
  /docs/{docId}:
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: docId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: byte
      responses:
        200:
          description: "200 OK"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/SimpleObj"
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/SimpleObj"
            application/vnd.restful+json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/SimpleObj"
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/SimpleObj"
components:
  schemas:
    SimpleObj:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
